	measure PerChange = ```
			
			VAR lastDatewData = MAXX(
			    FILTER(
			        'Date Table',
			        NOT(ISBLANK([Value_by_Product_Actual]))
			    ),
			    'Date Table'[Date]
			)
			
			VAR currentm = CALCULATE(
			    [Value_by_Product_Actual],
			    DATESMTD('Date Table'[Date])
			)
			
			VAR prevm = CALCULATE(
			    [Value_by_Product_Actual],
			    PREVIOUSMONTH('Date Table'[Date])
			)
			
			VAR perChange = CEILING(
			    IF(
			        NOT(ISBLANK(prevm)),
			        (currentm - prevm) / prevm,
			        0
			    ) * 100, 1
			)
			
			
			RETURN 
			    perChange
			    
			```
		displayFolder: Formating
		lineageTag: e5c51653-fa4f-4002-acc0-b727670e8e6d

		annotation PBI_FormatHint = {"isGeneralNumber":true}

